00:12:09,500 --> 00:12:11,250
getting a million followers

290
00:12:11,416 --> 00:12:13,250
having our face on a billboard

291
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:15,125
but what if the most meaningful

292
00:12:15,125 --> 00:12:17,333
life comes from bringing extraordinary presence

